{
  "stem": "8423.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was in the moments that I wasn't so totally depressed and wanted to die.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that this war would be over, and when the war would be over, I would go home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I would be with mother, and father, and with the children, the two little ones, and all this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was, you know, another voice telling me, but your mother is dead.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The two little ones are dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I wasn't listening.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I wasn't listening, because I didn't believe that my mother was dead.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And looking back, I know that that was my way to survive, thinking that they would be there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because if I had admitted to myself that mother would not be there, I am sure I would not have survived.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because that's what kept me going.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "When we finally arrived in Bergen-Belsen in March, and by that time, [DRINKS] things was so bad there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were really-- they were really following orders.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were scared to death with all these Germans who took over their house, kicked them out of their beds, took their food, you know, made them heat water for them to bathe, and everything.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then in one of the particular farmer's house, somehow my sister got in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was very, very brave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She did somethings that was so brave, it was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She got into the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she said, do you have any warm water for us?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the woman said, well, if, you know, there's any left, you can come in and wash.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I'm sure that was the water the Germans already washed in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because it did not look clean.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we weren't particular.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we took off our dress.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
